Package cscie97.asn1.knowledge.engine

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Importer
    This loads new Triples from an input file that gets manipulated by the KnowledgeGraph.
    KnowledgeGraph
    This is a database of Triples stored in memory.
    Node
    This is a Node, part of a Triple.
    Predicate
    This is the Predicate, part of the Triple.
    QueryEngine
    This is used to run queries on the KnowledgeGraph
    Triple
    This is a Triple, a subject (Node), predicate, and an object (Node) and the relationship stored in the KnowledgeGraph.
